src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 3 Midday' game
02 Nov 2019, 17:04 by The Associated Press
CLEVELAND (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday afternoon's drawing of the Ohio Lottery's "Pick 3 Midday" game were:
2-0-1
(two, zero, one)
